    <h3>Market Intelligence, Insights & Strategy</h3>

    <!-- <h5>Our Story</h5> -->
    <p>MLT Marketing Solutions provide strategic market research and competitive intelligence services to business-to-business and industrial clients. Some of our strategies include qualitative (face to face interviews, phone interviews, questionnaires) & quantitative methodologies...
        <br>
Great companies do not just break out overnight, it takes great customer insight and a deep understanding of the industry. With our services (Competitor intelligence, marketing sizing, marketing strategy & insights), we focus on building brands that last-long and meeting our customer needs. 
<br>

    </p>
    <br><br>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class=" double-text col-md-6">
            <h3>How we do it</h3>
            <p class="highlight-left">This is how we do it, we listen to the voice of your customers, find out what your competitors are doing, analyze the competitive landscape, discover and quantify new market opportunities, determine key decision-drivers and unmet needs, gather insights for product development and measure your brand equity.
We focus on the client’s objectives and we utilize sound classical research methodologies. MLT Marketing Solutions strives for insightful results high in validity, reliability, repeatability, and objectivity. 
Every challenge is <span class="boldit">special</span> to us; and our response to each is <span class="boldit">unique</span>
<br>
We target your strategic objectives to assist you to determine: <span class="boldit">Where you are… Where you would like to be…and a way to get there.</span>
</p>

        </div>  

