    <div class=" double-text col-md-6">
            <h3>Benefits of having MLT Solutions handle your Market Intelligence needs</h3>
           <p>
               <ul>
               <li>It allows you to make changes to products if necessary</li>
               <li>It gives you a clear understanding of your target audience and their needs.</li>
               <li>It reveals new opportunities in the market (new segment/products)</li>
               <li>Market Intelligence keeps your business up to date with your competitor’s successes and failures.</li>
               <li>It improves customer retention potential</li>
               <li>Having an in-depth understanding of your target audience reduces dependency on intuition and luck. </li>
               <li>It also informs your decisions, strategic direction in new product development and marketing.</li>
           </ul>    
           </p>
